text: Tylototriton shanorum is a newt endemic to Shan State, Myanmar, where it was recorded in Taunggyi. ==References== * Nishikawa, Matsui, & Rao, 2014 : A new species of Tylototriton (Amphibia: Urodela: Salamandridae) from central Myanmar. title: Tylototriton shanorum
